# Shared Packages

This monorepo contains several shared packages used across multiple applications.

## UI Package

- [packages/ui/](mdc:packages/ui) - Shared UI components
  - [packages/ui/src/components/](mdc:packages/ui/src/components) - Reusable UI components
  - [packages/ui/src/hooks/](mdc:packages/ui/src/hooks) - Custom React hooks
  - [packages/ui/src/primitives/](mdc:packages/ui/src/primitives) - Primitive UI elements

## Configuration Packages

- [packages/typescript-config/](mdc:packages/typescript-config) - Shared TypeScript configuration
- [packages/tailwind-config/](mdc:packages/tailwind-config) - Shared Tailwind CSS configuration

## Transactional Emails

- [packages/transactional/](mdc:packages/transactional) - Email templates
  - [packages/transactional/emails/](mdc:packages/transactional/emails) - Email templates
